<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom=
:5.75pt;
margin-left:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:150%'>Fashion Connect is a
specialized web-based platform designed to address the specific needs of
Malawi's local fashion designers by providing comprehensive e-commerce
infrastructure. The platform offers verified designer profiles, secure paym=
ent
processing through local mobile money services (Mpamba and Airtel Money), a=
nd
intelligent product discovery powered by vector search technology. By
implementing custom order management systems, escrow payment protection, and
personalized style recommendations, Fashion Connect overcomes the documented
limitations of general social media platforms for fashion transactions. This
solution builds trust between designers and clients through verification
processes, simplifies business operations for creatives, and creates a safe=
r marketplace
aligned with Malawi's digital economy strategy objectives.</p>

